                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The tashtari causes their filaments to glow with intense light. Non-tashtari creatures within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:40] must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:21] save. A creature that attempts this save is immune to all Bristle Flashes for 1 minute. The tashtari's fur then dims, and they can't use this ability until they bask in sunlight for at least 10 minutes.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Dazzled] for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is dazzled for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Blinded] for 1 round and dazzled for 1 minute.</p>"
