                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The tashtari alpha unleashes a searing, rainbow muzzle beam that soars into the sky before splitting into countless rays of multicolored light that crash down in every direction. Each non-tashtari creature in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:20] takes @Damage[4d6[fire]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:19|basic] save). On a critical failure, a creature that can see the tashtari alpha is also @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Dazzled] for 1 minute. Other tashtaris in the area recharge their Bristle Flash. The tashtari alpha's glowing heart dims, and they can't use this ability until they bask in sunlight for at least 1 hour.</p>"
